Package triple.com

Class PlanInstructor

java.lang.Object
triple.com.Plan
triple.com.PlanInstructor
public class PlanInstructor extends Plan
The PlanInstructor class extends the Plan class and represents a subscription plan for instructors. It adds functionality to manage instructors who subscribe to the plan and provides a method to view plan details.
